  <entry>
    <title>專題製作-神經網絡系統</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2024/10/22/%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C-%E7%A5%9E%E7%B6%93%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2024/10/22/%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C%E8%A3%BD%E4%BD%9C-%E7%A5%9E%E7%B6%93%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1/</id>
    <published>2024-10-22T12:28:32.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-10-31T10:43:32.962Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前情提要"><a href="#前情提要" class="headerlink" title="前情提要"></a>前情提要</h1><h3 id="這時得我還是一個很普通的高中生，連專案都沒有做過，平常也只會用python寫寫程式刷刷題而已，所以其實這次的專案花了我很多的時間…，在做的時候還一度懷疑自己到底能不能做出來。"><a href="#這時得我還是一個很普通的高中生，連專案都沒有做過，平常也只會用python寫寫程式刷刷題而已，所以其實這次的專案花了我很多的時間…，在做的時候還一度懷疑自己到底能不能做出來。" class="headerlink" title="這時得我還是一個很普通的高中生，連專案都沒有做過，平常也只會用python寫寫程式刷刷題而已，所以其實這次的專案花了我很多的時間…，在做的時候還一度懷疑自己到底能不能做出來。"></a>這時得我還是一個很普通的高中生，連專案都沒有做過，平常也只會用python寫寫程式刷刷題而已，所以其實這次的專案花了我很多的時間…，在做的時候還一度懷疑自己到底能不能做出來。</h3><h1 id="製作動機"><a href="#製作動機" class="headerlink" title="製作動機"></a>製作動機</h1><h3 id="因為校定必修要製作專題的關係所以就跟同學研究最近熱門的技術、時事，然後剛好那段時間剛度過疫情，而我們就思考疫情給我們帶來負面效果，我們就注意到了長時間上網課久坐，坐姿不良會給人們身體帶來一些疾病，所以我們就想解決這個問題，因此我們就確立主題了，而技術我們則是想選用影像辨識去辨識坐姿。"><a href="#因為校定必修要製作專題的關係所以就跟同學研究最近熱門的技術、時事，然後剛好那段時間剛度過疫情，而我們就思考疫情給我們帶來負面效果，我們就注意到了長時間上網課久坐，坐姿不良會給人們身體帶來一些疾病，所以我們就想解決這個問題，因此我們就確立主題了，而技術我們則是想選用影像辨識去辨識坐姿。" class="headerlink" title="因為校定必修要製作專題的關係所以就跟同學研究最近熱門的技術、時事，然後剛好那段時間剛度過疫情，而我們就思考疫情給我們帶來負面效果，我們就注意到了長時間上網課久坐，坐姿不良會給人們身體帶來一些疾病，所以我們就想解決這個問題，因此我們就確立主題了，而技術我們則是想選用影像辨識去辨識坐姿。"></a>因為校定必修要製作專題的關係所以就跟同學研究最近熱門的技術、時事，然後剛好那段時間剛度過疫情，而我們就思考疫情給我們帶來負面效果，我們就注意到了長時間上網課久坐，坐姿不良會給人們身體帶來一些疾病，所以我們就想解決這個問題，因此我們就確立主題了，而技術我們則是想選用影像辨識去辨識坐姿。</h3><h1 id="opencv"><a href="#opencv" class="headerlink" title="opencv"></a>opencv</h1><h3 id="一開始找資料是找到了opencv這個技術，然後我對這個技術完全沒有一些概念，所以就先上網查資料看看這東西到底怎麼用，之後找到了這個影片"><a href="#一開始找資料是找到了opencv這個技術，然後我對這個技術完全沒有一些概念，所以就先上網查資料看看這東西到底怎麼用，之後找到了這個影片" class="headerlink" title="一開始找資料是找到了opencv這個技術，然後我對這個技術完全沒有一些概念，所以就先上網查資料看看這東西到底怎麼用，之後找到了這個影片"></a>一開始找資料是找到了opencv這個技術，然後我對這個技術完全沒有一些概念，所以就先上網查資料看看這東西到底怎麼用，之後找到了這個影片</h3><h4 id="opencv2小時初學者教學-https-www-youtube-com-watch-v-xjrykYpaBBM-ab-channel-GrandmaCan-E6-88-91-E9-98-BF-E5-AC-A4-E9-83-BD-E6-9C-83"><a href="#opencv2小時初學者教學-https-www-youtube-com-watch-v-xjrykYpaBBM-ab-channel-GrandmaCan-E6-88-91-E9-98-BF-E5-AC-A4-E9-83-BD-E6-9C-83" class="headerlink" title="[opencv2小時初學者教學]https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xjrykYpaBBM&amp;ab_channel=GrandmaCan-%E6%88%91%E9%98%BF%E5%AC%A4%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83"></a>[opencv2小時初學者教學]<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xjrykYpaBBM&ab_channel=GrandmaCan-%E6%88%91%E9%98%BF%E5%AC%A4%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xjrykYpaBBM&amp;ab_channel=GrandmaCan-%E6%88%91%E9%98%BF%E5%AC%A4%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%83</a></h4><h3 id="最一開始我想說都跟著影片一起做，而我在影片的最開頭我就卡住了…，因為這影片是比較久以前的，而opencv的函式又已經更新了導致有些語法不一樣，再加上我又是做專案的新手XD-那時候的我連pip都不知道-，所以就卡了超級久，後來是換了opencv的版本才可以繼續跟著做，然後這是我學到的第一個terminal-“pip-install-Opencv-python”。"><a href="#最一開始我想說都跟著影片一起做，而我在影片的最開頭我就卡住了…，因為這影片是比較久以前的，而opencv的函式又已經更新了導致有些語法不一樣，再加上我又是做專案的新手XD-那時候的我連pip都不知道-，所以就卡了超級久，後來是換了opencv的版本才可以繼續跟著做，然後這是我學到的第一個terminal-“pip-install-Opencv-python”。" class="headerlink" title="最一開始我想說都跟著影片一起做，而我在影片的最開頭我就卡住了…，因為這影片是比較久以前的，而opencv的函式又已經更新了導致有些語法不一樣，再加上我又是做專案的新手XD(那時候的我連pip都不知道)，所以就卡了超級久，後來是換了opencv的版本才可以繼續跟著做，然後這是我學到的第一個terminal “pip install Opencv-python”。"></a>最一開始我想說都跟著影片一起做，而我在影片的最開頭我就卡住了…，因為這影片是比較久以前的，而opencv的函式又已經更新了導致有些語法不一樣，再加上我又是做專案的新手XD(那時候的我連pip都不知道)，所以就卡了超級久，後來是換了opencv的版本才可以繼續跟著做，然後這是我學到的第一個terminal “pip install Opencv-python”。</h3><h3 id="從這影片大概可以了解基礎的opencv語法，我在裡面注意到臉部偵測這個，我認為它可以偵測臉部輪廓、物體輪廓，那他正常來說也可以去偵測坐姿。"><a href="#從這影片大概可以了解基礎的opencv語法，我在裡面注意到臉部偵測這個，我認為它可以偵測臉部輪廓、物體輪廓，那他正常來說也可以去偵測坐姿。" class="headerlink" title="從這影片大概可以了解基礎的opencv語法，我在裡面注意到臉部偵測這個，我認為它可以偵測臉部輪廓、物體輪廓，那他正常來說也可以去偵測坐姿。"></a>從這影片大概可以了解基礎的opencv語法，我在裡面注意到臉部偵測這個，我認為它可以偵測臉部輪廓、物體輪廓，那他正常來說也可以去偵測坐姿。</h3><p><img src="https://hackmd.io/_uploads/HJqAf9IeJe.png" alt="偵測輪廓"></p><h3 id="還有另一個比較重要的是導入模型，用模型偵測東西旁邊就會跑出框框，但要根據偵測的東西去調整模型"><a href="#還有另一個比較重要的是導入模型，用模型偵測東西旁邊就會跑出框框，但要根據偵測的東西去調整模型" class="headerlink" title="還有另一個比較重要的是導入模型，用模型偵測東西旁邊就會跑出框框，但要根據偵測的東西去調整模型"></a>還有另一個比較重要的是導入模型，用模型偵測東西旁邊就會跑出框框，但要根據偵測的東西去調整模型</h3><p><img src="https://hackmd.io/_uploads/ByVAHcIlkg.png" alt="模型導入"></p><h1 id="openpose"><a href="#openpose" class="headerlink" title="openpose"></a>openpose</h1><h3 id="之後經過了一頓的搜尋之後又看到了openpose這個模型，而我們看到他的模型似乎比較完整，所以就對openpose做更深入的了解。"><a href="#之後經過了一頓的搜尋之後又看到了openpose這個模型，而我們看到他的模型似乎比較完整，所以就對openpose做更深入的了解。" class="headerlink" title="之後經過了一頓的搜尋之後又看到了openpose這個模型，而我們看到他的模型似乎比較完整，所以就對openpose做更深入的了解。"></a>之後經過了一頓的搜尋之後又看到了openpose這個模型，而我們看到他的模型似乎比較完整，所以就對openpose做更深入的了解。</h3><p><img src="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1200/1*eWOzEMXjCtErKJBXfhGTkg.png" alt="openpose"></p><h3 id="但結果我們開始實作時才發現要用這個模型超級麻煩…。要用我不熟悉的cpp編譯，還要用沒接觸過的cmake，之後又因為一大堆的硬體關係所以放棄了這條路。"><a href="#但結果我們開始實作時才發現要用這個模型超級麻煩…。要用我不熟悉的cpp編譯，還要用沒接觸過的cmake，之後又因為一大堆的硬體關係所以放棄了這條路。" class="headerlink" title="但結果我們開始實作時才發現要用這個模型超級麻煩…。要用我不熟悉的cpp編譯，還要用沒接觸過的cmake，之後又因為一大堆的硬體關係所以放棄了這條路。"></a>但結果我們開始實作時才發現要用這個模型超級麻煩…。要用我不熟悉的cpp編譯，還要用沒接觸過的cmake，之後又因為一大堆的硬體關係所以放棄了這條路。</h3><h1 id="再度回到opencv"><a href="#再度回到opencv" class="headerlink" title="再度回到opencv"></a>再度回到opencv</h1><h3 id="結果繞來繞去最後還是回到了用opencv。而我們是用網路上提供的模型去做測試。"><a href="#結果繞來繞去最後還是回到了用opencv。而我們是用網路上提供的模型去做測試。" class="headerlink" title="結果繞來繞去最後還是回到了用opencv。而我們是用網路上提供的模型去做測試。"></a>結果繞來繞去最後還是回到了用opencv。而我們是用網路上提供的模型去做測試。</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">graph_opt.pb</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://hackmd.io/_uploads/Sk87fJugye.png" alt="graph_opt.pb"></p><h3 id="之後就真正開始實作了，一開始就先pip-opencv"><a href="#之後就真正開始實作了，一開始就先pip-opencv" class="headerlink" title="之後就真正開始實作了，一開始就先pip opencv"></a>之後就真正開始實作了，一開始就先pip opencv</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install opencv-python-headless</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="接著引入cv2-然後定義一些基礎的變數、等等的。"><a href="#接著引入cv2-然後定義一些基礎的變數、等等的。" class="headerlink" title="接著引入cv2 然後定義一些基礎的變數、等等的。"></a>接著引入cv2 然後定義一些基礎的變數、等等的。</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import cv2</span><br><span class="line">import numpy as np</span><br><span class="line">net = cv2.dnn.readNetFromTensorflow(<span class="string">&#x27;graph_opt.pb&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cap</span> = cv2.VideoCapture(0)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="定義人體各個關節點的位置、名稱"><a href="#定義人體各個關節點的位置、名稱" class="headerlink" title="定義人體各個關節點的位置、名稱"></a>定義人體各個關節點的位置、名稱</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">POSE_PAIRS = [</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 頭部到軀幹</span></span><br><span class="line">    (0, 1),</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 脊椎</span></span><br><span class="line">    (1, 7), (7, 8), (8, 9), <span class="comment"># 從軀幹頂部到腰部的三個脊椎關鍵點</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 腰部</span></span><br><span class="line">    (9, 10), </span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 右腿</span></span><br><span class="line">    (10, 11), (11, 12),</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 左腿</span></span><br><span class="line">    (10, 13), (13, 14)</span><br><span class="line">]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="之後開始寫判斷條件-把人體的模型都描繪出來"><a href="#之後開始寫判斷條件-把人體的模型都描繪出來" class="headerlink" title="之後開始寫判斷條件 把人體的模型都描繪出來"></a>之後開始寫判斷條件 把人體的模型都描繪出來</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">threshold = 0.1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> True:</span><br><span class="line">    ret, frame = cap.read()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> not ret:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">break</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 對捕獲到的影像進行處理</span></span><br><span class="line">    frame_blob = cv2.dnn.blobFromImage(frame, 1.0, (368, 368), (127.5, 127.5, 127.5), swapRB=True, crop=False)</span><br><span class="line">    net.setInput(frame_blob)</span><br><span class="line">    output = net.forward()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    h, w = frame.shape[:2]</span><br><span class="line">    points = []</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> range(output.shape[1]):</span><br><span class="line">        probMap = output[0, i, :, :]</span><br><span class="line">        minVal, prob, minLoc, point = cv2.minMaxLoc(probMap)</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        x = (w * point[0]) / output.shape[3]</span><br><span class="line">        y = (h * point[1]) / output.shape[2]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> prob &gt; threshold:</span><br><span class="line">            points.append((int(x), int(y)))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            points.append(None)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> pair <span class="keyword">in</span> POSE_PAIRS:</span><br><span class="line">        partA = pair[0]</span><br><span class="line">        partB = pair[1]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> points[partA] and points[partB]:</span><br><span class="line">            cv2.line(frame, points[partA], points[partB], (0, 255, 0), 2)</span><br><span class="line">            cv2.circle(frame, points[partA], 5, (0, 255, 0), -1)</span><br><span class="line">            cv2.circle(frame, points[partB], 5, (0, 255, 0), -1)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 顯示結果</span></span><br><span class="line">    cv2.imshow(<span class="string">&#x27;Keypoints and Skeleton&#x27;</span>, frame)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 按下 &#x27;q&#x27; 鍵退出迴圈</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> cv2.waitKey(1) &amp; 0xFF == ord(<span class="string">&#x27; &#x27;</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">break</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 釋放攝像頭</span></span><br><span class="line">cap.release()</span><br><span class="line">cv2.destroyAllWindows()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="然後就發現-出事了XD"><a href="#然後就發現-出事了XD" class="headerlink" title="然後就發現. 出事了XD"></a>然後就發現. 出事了XD</h3><p><img src="https://hackmd.io/_uploads/SJo4VcgbJe.png" alt="image"></p><h3 id="推斷出有兩種問題-1-模型出現問題-2-邏輯判斷出現問題，因為保險起見的關係所以把兩種都改掉了，模型換成mediapipe的-優點是比較輕量化-同時又比較準確。"><a href="#推斷出有兩種問題-1-模型出現問題-2-邏輯判斷出現問題，因為保險起見的關係所以把兩種都改掉了，模型換成mediapipe的-優點是比較輕量化-同時又比較準確。" class="headerlink" title="推斷出有兩種問題 1.模型出現問題 2.邏輯判斷出現問題，因為保險起見的關係所以把兩種都改掉了，模型換成mediapipe的 優點是比較輕量化 同時又比較準確。"></a>推斷出有兩種問題 1.模型出現問題 2.邏輯判斷出現問題，因為保險起見的關係所以把兩種都改掉了，模型換成mediapipe的 優點是比較輕量化 同時又比較準確。</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">import cv2</span><br><span class="line">import mediapipe as mp</span><br><span class="line">import numpy as np</span><br><span class="line">import time</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="然後再加上坐姿不良的判斷，分別分為坐姿傾斜、翹腳、盤腿這幾種坐姿不良。"><a href="#然後再加上坐姿不良的判斷，分別分為坐姿傾斜、翹腳、盤腿這幾種坐姿不良。" class="headerlink" title="然後再加上坐姿不良的判斷，分別分為坐姿傾斜、翹腳、盤腿這幾種坐姿不良。"></a>然後再加上坐姿不良的判斷，分別分為坐姿傾斜、翹腳、盤腿這幾種坐姿不良。</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br><span class="line">78</span><br><span class="line">79</span><br><span class="line">80</span><br><span class="line">81</span><br><span class="line">82</span><br><span class="line">83</span><br><span class="line">84</span><br><span class="line">85</span><br><span class="line">86</span><br><span class="line">87</span><br><span class="line">88</span><br><span class="line">89</span><br><span class="line">90</span><br><span class="line">91</span><br><span class="line">92</span><br><span class="line">93</span><br><span class="line">94</span><br><span class="line">95</span><br><span class="line">96</span><br><span class="line">97</span><br><span class="line">98</span><br><span class="line">99</span><br><span class="line">100</span><br><span class="line">101</span><br><span class="line">102</span><br><span class="line">103</span><br><span class="line">104</span><br><span class="line">105</span><br><span class="line">106</span><br><span class="line">107</span><br><span class="line">108</span><br><span class="line">109</span><br><span class="line">110</span><br><span class="line">111</span><br><span class="line">112</span><br><span class="line">113</span><br><span class="line">114</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">with mp_holistic.Holistic(min_detection_confidence=0.5, min_tracking_confidence=0.5) as holistic:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> not cap.isOpened():</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Cannot open camera&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">exit</span>()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> True:</span><br><span class="line">        ret, img = cap.read()</span><br><span class="line">        ret_gif, frame_gif = cap_gif.read()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> not ret:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Cannot receive frame&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">break</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> not ret_gif:</span><br><span class="line">            cap_gif.set(cv2.CAP_PROP_POS_FRAMES, 0)</span><br><span class="line">            ret_gif, frame_gif = cap_gif.read()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        img = cv2.resize(img, (1280, 960))</span><br><span class="line">        frame_gif_resized = cv2.resize(frame_gif, (800, 640))</span><br><span class="line">        img2 = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)</span><br><span class="line">        results = holistic.process(img2)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        mp_drawing.draw_landmarks(img, results.face_landmarks, mp_holistic.FACEMESH_CONTOURS,</span><br><span class="line">                                  landmark_drawing_spec=None, connection_drawing_spec=mp_drawing_styles.get_default_face_mesh_contours_style())</span><br><span class="line">        mp_drawing.draw_landmarks(img, results.pose_landmarks, mp_holistic.POSE_CONNECTIONS,</span><br><span class="line">                                  landmark_drawing_spec=mp_drawing_styles.get_default_pose_landmarks_style())</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> results.pose_landmarks:</span><br><span class="line">            posture_warnings = []</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment"># Extract landmark positions</span></span><br><span class="line">            left_shoulder = [results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.LEFT_SHOULDER.value].x,</span><br><span class="line">                             results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.LEFT_SHOULDER.value].y]</span><br><span class="line">            right_shoulder = [results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.RIGHT_SHOULDER.value].x,</span><br><span class="line">                              results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.RIGHT_SHOULDER.value].y]</span><br><span class="line">            left_hip = [results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.LEFT_HIP.value].x,</span><br><span class="line">                        results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.LEFT_HIP.value].y]</span><br><span class="line">            right_hip = [results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.RIGHT_HIP.value].x,</span><br><span class="line">                         results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.RIGHT_HIP.value].y]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment"># Calculate midpoints for shoulders and hips</span></span><br><span class="line">            shoulder_midpoint = [(left_shoulder[0] + right_shoulder[0]) / 2, </span><br><span class="line">                                 (left_shoulder[1] + right_shoulder[1]) / 2]</span><br><span class="line">            hip_midpoint = [(left_hip[0] + right_hip[0]) / 2, </span><br><span class="line">                            (left_hip[1] + right_hip[1]) / 2]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            left_ankle = [results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.LEFT_ANKLE.value].x,</span><br><span class="line">                          results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.LEFT_ANKLE.value].y]</span><br><span class="line">            right_ankle = [results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.RIGHT_ANKLE.value].x,</span><br><span class="line">                           results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.RIGHT_ANKLE.value].y]</span><br><span class="line">            nose = [results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.NOSE.value].x,</span><br><span class="line">                    results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.NOSE.value].y]</span><br><span class="line">            left_knee = [results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.LEFT_KNEE.value].x,</span><br><span class="line">                         results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.LEFT_KNEE.value].y]</span><br><span class="line">            right_knee = [results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.RIGHT_KNEE.value].x,</span><br><span class="line">                          results.pose_landmarks.landmark[mp_holistic.PoseLandmark.RIGHT_KNEE.value].y]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment"># Calculate differences for pose detection</span></span><br><span class="line">            shoulder_diff = abs(left_shoulder[1] - right_shoulder[1])</span><br><span class="line">            hip_level_diff = abs(left_hip[1] - right_hip[1])</span><br><span class="line">            left_ankle_diff = abs(left_hip[1] - left_ankle[1])</span><br><span class="line">            right_ankle_diff = abs(right_hip[1] - right_ankle[1])</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment"># Calculate the average vertical distance from nose to both knees</span></span><br><span class="line">            avg_knee_y = (left_knee[1] + right_knee[1]) / 2</span><br><span class="line">            nose_to_knee_distance = abs(nose[1] - avg_knee_y)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            forward_leaning_threshold = 0.265  <span class="comment"># This threshold might need adjustment based on testing</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> nose_to_knee_distance &lt; forward_leaning_threshold:</span><br><span class="line">                posture_warnings.append(<span class="string">&quot;Forward Leaning&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment"># Calculate distance between both ankles</span></span><br><span class="line">            ankle_distance = ((right_ankle[<span class="number">0</span>] - left_ankle[<span class="number">0</span>])**<span class="number">2</span> + (right_ankle[<span class="number">1</span>] - left_ankle[<span class="number">1</span>])**<span class="number">2</span>)**<span class="number">0.5</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            if shoulder_diff &gt; <span class="number">0.02</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                posture_warnings.append(&quot;Shoulder Tilt&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">            if hip_level_diff &gt; <span class="number">0.02</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                posture_warnings.append(&quot;Sideways Bend&quot;)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            # Check for cross-legged sitting</span><br><span class="line">            if left_ankle_diff &lt; <span class="number">0.1</span> and right_ankle_diff &lt; <span class="number">0.1</span> and ankle_distance &lt; <span class="number">0.2</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                posture_warnings.append(&quot;Sitting Cross-legged&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">                color = (<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)  # Green</span><br><span class="line">            elif left_ankle_diff &lt; <span class="number">0.1</span> or right_ankle_diff &lt; <span class="number">0.1</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                posture_warnings.append(&quot;Legs Crossed&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">                color = (<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">255</span>)  # Red</span><br><span class="line">                last_warning_time = time.time()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            combined_warnings = &quot;, &quot;.join(posture_warnings)</span><br><span class="line">            if posture_warnings:</span><br><span class="line">                combined_img = np.zeros((<span class="number">960</span> + <span class="number">640</span>, <span class="number">1280</span>, <span class="number">3</span>), dtype=np.uint8)</span><br><span class="line">                combined_img[:<span class="number">960</span>, :] = img</span><br><span class="line">                combined_img[<span class="number">960</span>:, <span class="number">240</span>:<span class="number">1040</span>] = frame_gif_resized</span><br><span class="line">                img = combined_img</span><br><span class="line">            if &quot;Legs Crossed&quot; in combined_warnings and &quot;Sitting Cross-legged&quot; not in combined_warnings:</span><br><span class="line">                color = (<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">255</span>)  # Red</span><br><span class="line">                last_warning_time = time.time()</span><br><span class="line">            elif time.time() - last_warning_time &lt; <span class="number">3</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                color = (<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">165</span>, <span class="number">255</span>)  # Orange</span><br><span class="line">            else:</span><br><span class="line">                color = (<span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">255</span>, <span class="number">0</span>)  # Green</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            # Get nose position in pixel coordinates</span><br><span class="line">            nose_pixel = mp_drawing._normalized_to_pixel_coordinates(nose[<span class="number">0</span>], nose[<span class="number">1</span>], <span class="number">1280</span>, <span class="number">960</span>)</span><br><span class="line">            if nose_pixel:</span><br><span class="line">                text_position = (nose_pixel[<span class="number">0</span>] - <span class="number">400</span>, nose_pixel[<span class="number">1</span>])</span><br><span class="line">                cv2.putText(img, combined_warnings, text_position, cv2.FONT_HERSHEY_SIMPLEX, <span class="number">1</span>, color, <span class="number">2</span>, cv2.LINE_AA)</span><br><span class="line">            if nose_pixel is None:</span><br><span class="line">                print(&quot;Nose pixel conversion failed!&quot;)</span><br><span class="line">                continue  # Skip the rest of the loop iteration</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            # Set text position to the left of the nose</span><br><span class="line">            text_position = (nose_pixel[<span class="number">0</span>] - <span class="number">400</span>, nose_pixel[<span class="number">1</span>])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">            cv2.putText(img, combined_warnings, text_position, cv2.FONT_HERSHEY_SIMPLEX, <span class="number">1</span>, color, <span class="number">2</span>, cv2.LINE_AA)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="之後就大概正常了-再根據細部內容調整閥值"><a href="#之後就大概正常了-再根據細部內容調整閥值" class="headerlink" title="之後就大概正常了 再根據細部內容調整閥值"></a>之後就大概正常了 再根據細部內容調整閥值</h3><p><img src="https://hackmd.io/_uploads/H1D0Kqlbkg.png" alt="image"></p><h3 id="而因